# Weather Maps & Tiled Layers

Included in [Weather maps API](https://www.meteosource.com/documentation#map)

Available for [Standard and Flexi plans](https://www.meteosource.com/pricing)

Receive various weather map layers for current and forecasted weather. You can choose from the most useful variables and obtain all data using one simple URL.

Global radar, temperature, rain, clouds and other variables are available in high-resolution and are ready to be overlaid within mapping applications for easy implementation.

